Package org.jamsim.ascape.output

Ascape simulation output.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChartProvider
    Provides a chart type and series to create a ChartView.
    MultiRunOutputDatasetProvider
    A OutputDatasetProvider that provides a multiple run dataset.
    OutputDatasetDefs<D extends ScapeData>
    Defines a series of output datasets to be attached to a MicroSimScape .
    OutputDatasetProvider
    Provider of a simulation output dataset for a given run number.
    Saveable
    A Saveable object.
    StatCollectorProvider
    Provider of a collection of StatCollectors.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Abstract1DMultiRunOutputDataset
    Implementation of MultiRunOutputDatasetProvider based on an array of doubles.
    MeansOnMultiRunDataset
    Executes ScapeRInterface.meanOfRuns(CDataCacheContainer, String, String) on a MultiRunOutputDatasetProvider.
    REXPDatasetProvider
    Provides a pre-existing REXP as a dataset.
    ROutput
    A single run output dataset produced by running commands on the scape dataframe.
    ROutput1DMultiRun
    An output dataset produced by running commands on the scape dataframe in R.
    SaveableDataset
    A Saveable CDataCacheContainer.
    StatsRowsChartProvider
    A ChartProvider derived from a StatsRows object.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    OutputException
    Generic exception that signals a problem with the creation of output data.
